commit.title: Add some test-suite files.
commit.message:
Add some test-suite files.

Our new implementation of eauto maintains compatibility mostly,
so #6544 is still open.

However, our implementation of the using clause just adds hints exactly
as adding them to a hint database would so this closes #6198.
